**********************************************************
* Before using xine_d4d_plugin, you must create symbolic *
* links to specify the device nodes of your DVD drive.   *
*                                                        *
* example:                                               *
*   ln -s /dev/acd0c /dev/dvd                            *
*   ln -s /dev/racd0c /dev/rdvd  (on -stable)            *
*                                                        *
*   ln -s /dev/acd0c /dev/dvd                            *
*   ln -s /dev/acd0c /dev/rdvd   (on -current)           *
**********************************************************
